Error [ESAZ0374005]: A Final may not be used in this way
    --> compiler-test:12:30
     |
  12 |         let start_2: Final = start.1;
     |                              ^^^^^^^
     |
     = Finals should be created, assigned to a variable, and consumed without being moved or reassigned.
Warning [WCEI03713004]: Value `start` used in finalize block is derived from external call `credits.aleo/transfer_private_to_public`, whose finalize may alter the state this value depends on.
    --> compiler-test:16:17
     |
  16 |                 start.1.run();
     |                 ^^^^^
     |
     = The external program's finalize runs concurrently and may invalidate assumptions based on this value. Consider re-reading the value on-chain inside the finalize block.
